<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Your Voter Credentials - VOTE4ME</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4A90D9 0%, #357ABD 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
        .content { padding: 30px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #4A90D9; color: white !important; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; }
        .credentials-box { background: #f0f7ff; padding: 20px; border: 2px solid #4A90D9; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .credentials-box p { margin: 10px 0; }
        .credentials-box code { background: #fff; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; background: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .warning { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .warning strong { color: #856404; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üó≥Ô∏è VOTE4ME</h1>
            <p>Your Voice Matters</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome, {{voterName}}!</h2>
            <p>You have been registered as a voter at <strong>{{schoolName}}</strong>.</p>

            <p>Your voting credentials are:</p>

            <div class="credentials-box">
                <p><strong>Voter ID:</strong></p>
                <p><code>{{voterId}}</code></p>
                <br>
                <p><strong>Secret Code:</strong></p>
                <p><code>{{secretCode}}</code></p>
            </div>

            <div class="warning">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Security Notice:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Keep your secret code confidential</li>
                    <li>Never share your credentials with anyone</li>
                    <li>You will need both your Voter ID and Secret Code to vote</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{votingUrl}}" class="button">Go to Voting Portal</a>
            </p>

            <p>When voting opens, use your credentials to log in and cast your vote.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from VOTE4ME voting system.</p>
            <p>If you did not register for voting, please contact your school administrator.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

